INSERT INTO illusts (
                    id,
                    title,
                    author_id,
                    create_date,
                    update_date,
                    x_restrict,
                    ai_type,
                    illust_state,
                    bookmark_id,
                    bookmark_private,
                    illust_type,
                    page_count,
                    last_fetch
                ) VALUES (
                    ?, ?, ?, datetime(?, 'utc'), datetime(?, 'utc'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, datetime('now', 'utc')
                )
